import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const NewTweet = () => {
    const header_border = {
        borderBottom: "1px solid #38444D",
      };
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Box w="600px" h="120px" style={header_border} ml="-17px" bg="tomato">
                <Stack direction="column">
                    <Box>
                        <Stack direction="row">

                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Stack direction="row">
                            <Box>
                                <Stack direction="row"></Stack>
                            </Box>
                            <Box></Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Box>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default NewTweet
